headline: CHIPOTLE LAUNCHES "INGREDIENT QUEST" EXPERIENCE ON ROBLOX AND MORE THAN $1 MILLION IN FREE CHIPOTLE FOR CINCO DE MAYO
summary: Chipotle Mexican Grill (NYSE: CMG) today announced it is celebrating Cinco de Mayo with five days of real food, real fun and real prizes. On Cinco de Mayo, the brand is launching a new, immersive digital gaming experience, "Ingredient Quest," in the Burrito Builder experience on Roblox, which challenges users to collect virtual cards featuring Chipotle's 53 ingredients for the opportunity to win free burritos.

headline: Chipotle's Sales Just Dropped for the First Time Since 2020. What Should Investors Do Now?
summary: Whether it's for a burrito, guacamole, or something else, diners have consistently gone out to eat at Chipotle Mexican Grill (NYSE: CMG) more and more over the last 10 years.  Of course, there was an exception to this trend at the outset of the COVID-19 pandemic -- comparable sales were down nearly 10% in the second quarter of 2020.  Chipotle's comparable sales have increased year over year in every quarter since the second quarter of 2020.
